<br>
the channel is FOWT. To join u simply type /join FOWT and then type /1 before your text to talk in the channel.<br>
<br>
By using this channel we can communicate with people from Wolves of Twilight and hopefully get some groups up and going before we start on raids and the like. We all need to get to know each other, in this guild and in WoT if we are going to run successful raids, becasue we will need to know and trust each other in potentially stressful situations. So far no-one has said they do not wish us to have an alliance, tho the decision still has to be made about whether we will or not - this exercise may help u too make that decision) You may get the opportunity to group or just chat with some of the peeps in the guild and then know whether the allince will be of benefit or not.....<br>
<br>
Please help to make this a successful exercise)<br>
It just takes a few seconds of your time to log in to the channel when you get online. And then u can use it as u would the guild window.<br>
<br>
Give it a try and then let us know how u feel about it) As always this is *your* guild and your opinions do matter.<br>
<br>
Leebe<br>
