It seems however that there isnt an ingame command to de-autojoin a channel.<br>
<br>
The best way to do this is by editing the EQclient.ini file thats located in the directory where you have installed everquest.<br>
When you have opened this file in a text-editor, look for a line called ChannelAutoJoin=xxxx (x meaning the name of the channel). By deleting this line the autojoin will be cancelled.<br>
